	BugsHunter v0.2 Web Exploiting Framework
	
	It help you to find and try web vulnerabilities.
	
	
Commands:

	pwd 					-> 	Print Working Directory.
	edit					->	Open Xterm with your favourite editor.
	sh					->	Launch sh commands.
	set 					->	Set variables in conf file.
	search					->	Search vulnz in source code.
	tree					->	Show all files in a tree view.
	quit					->	Quit.